29213a71-f8ef-485c-9ee7-c41787b0eeb3	snake-bites	Snake Bites	"[{\\"id\\":\\"5877f4b3-c269-4075-b1ad-988f70d333eb\\",\\"type\\":\\"heading\\",\\"props\\":{\\"textColor\\":\\"default\\",\\"backgroundColor\\":\\"default\\",\\"textAlignment\\":\\"left\\",\\"level\\":3},\\"content\\":[{\\"type\\":\\"text\\",\\"text\\":\\"IMMEDIATE FIRST AID for bites by Bothrops species of Central & South America\\",\\"styles\\":{}}],\\"children\\":[]},{\\"id\\":\\"7bcfed40-6773-450e-b615-250cb987d2d2\\",\\"type\\":\\"numberedListItem\\",\\"props\\":{\\"textColor\\":\\"default\\",\\"backgroundColor\\":\\"default\\",\\"textAlignment\\":\\"left\\"},\\"content\\":[{\\"type\\":\\"text\\",\\"text\\":\\"Take photo of the snake (head and body) if safe to do so.\\",\\"styles\\":{}}],\\"children\\":[]},{\\"id\\":\\"99db0cdb-ca73-43c5-af24-b0ca4ea53321\\",\\"type\\":\\"numberedListItem\\",\\"props\\":{\\"textColor\\":\\"default\\",\\"backgroundColor\\":\\"default\\",\\"textAlignment\\":\\"left\\"},\\"content\\":[{\\"type\\":\\"text\\",\\"text\\":\\"Keep the victim calm and reassured. Allow him or her to lie flat and avoid as much movement as possible. If possible, allow the bitten limb to rest at a level lower than the victim's heart.\\",\\"styles\\":{}}],\\"children\\":[]},{\\"id\\":\\"c3c0b9fa-ba20-46ab-b8e3-090e53d09ab2\\",\\"type\\":\\"numberedListItem\\",\\"props\\":{\\"textColor\\":\\"default\\",\\"backgroundColor\\":\\"default\\",\\"textAlignment\\":\\"left\\"},\\"content\\":[{\\"type\\":\\"text\\",\\"text\\":\\"Identify the bite site, looking for fang marks, and apply the Sawyer Pump extractor with the largest cup possible over the bite site. If there are two or more fang marks noted on the limb, apply the pump extractor over at least one fang mark. If more than one pump extractor is available, they may be applied to the additional fang marks.\\",\\"styles\\":{}}],\\"children\\":[]},{\\"id\\":\\"00f66ed4-f508-4746-bc23-f0ba08952eaf\\",\\"type\\":\\"numberedListItem\\",\\"props\\":{\\"textColor\\":\\"default\\",\\"backgroundColor\\":\\"default\\",\\"textAlignment\\":\\"left\\"},\\"content\\":[{\\"type\\":\\"text\\",\\"text\\":\\"Immediately wrap a large constricting band snugly about the bitten limb at a level just above the bite site, ie. between the bite site and the heart. The constricting band should be as tight as one might bind a sprained ankle, but not so tight as to constrict blood flow.\\",\\"styles\\":{}}],\\"children\\":[]},{\\"id\\":\\"0efdbde4-554a-49fe-8294-0d76b1a44c3b\\",\\"type\\":\\"numberedListItem\\",\\"props\\":{\\"textColor\\":\\"default\\",\\"backgroundColor\\":\\"default\\",\\"textAlignment\\":\\"left\\"},\\"content\\":[{\\"type\\":\\"text\\",\\"text\\":\\"DO NOT remove the constricting band until the victim has reached the hospital and is receiving antivenom.\\",\\"styles\\":{}}],\\"children\\":[]},{\\"id\\":\\"9192c994-0a46-43a5-8506-f792dea76089\\",\\"type\\":\\"numberedListItem\\",\\"props\\":{\\"textColor\\":\\"default\\",\\"backgroundColor\\":\\"default\\",\\"textAlignment\\":\\"left\\"},\\"content\\":[{\\"type\\":\\"text\\",\\"text\\":\\"Have the Wyeth Crotalidae Polyvalent Antivenom (NOTE: THIS ANTIVENOM IS ONLY FOR BOTHROPS SPECIES) ready for the emergency crew to take with the victim to the hospital. Give them the following:\\",\\"styles\\":{}}],\\"children\\":[]},{\\"id\\":\\"0a6025b0-ed68-4df2-bef7-c2d3614b7281\\",\\"type\\":\\"numberedListItem\\",\\"props\\":{\\"textColor\\":\\"default\\",\\"backgroundColor\\":\\"default\\",\\"textAlignment\\":\\"left\\"},\\"content\\":[{\\"type\\":\\"text\\",\\"text\\":\\"the available antivenom (at least 20 vials)\\",\\"styles\\":{}}],\\"children\\":[]},{\\"id\\":\\"91094ded-35e4-4b8a-bdc2-8c8eabeaaa23\\",\\"type\\":\\"numberedListItem\\",\\"props\\":{\\"textColor\\":\\"default\\",\\"backgroundColor\\":\\"default\\",\\"textAlignment\\":\\"left\\"},\\"content\\":[{\\"type\\":\\"text\\",\\"text\\":\\"the accompanying instruction (Protocol) packet\\",\\"styles\\":{}}],\\"children\\":[]},{\\"id\\":\\"5faf6a6f-9c21-4521-8c5b-f4c014467124\\",\\"type\\":\\"numberedListItem\\",\\"props\\":{\\"textColor\\":\\"default\\",\\"backgroundColor\\":\\"default\\",\\"textAlignment\\":\\"left\\"},\\"content\\":[{\\"type\\":\\"text\\",\\"text\\":\\"the victim's medical packet (if available)\\",\\"styles\\":{}}],\\"children\\":[]},{\\"id\\":\\"68e91ecf-8bfb-4cac-98d8-41dda50d8cb9\\",\\"type\\":\\"paragraph\\",\\"props\\":{\\"textColor\\":\\"default\\",\\"backgroundColor\\":\\"default\\",\\"textAlignment\\":\\"left\\"},\\"content\\":[{\\"type\\":\\"text\\",\\"text\\":\\"DO NOT cut or incise the bite site. DO NOT apply ice to the bite site.\\",\\"styles\\":{\\"textColor\\":\\"red\\"}}],\\"children\\":[]},{\\"id\\":\\"6dd0b575-9083-4246-99c4-9c527ff33630\\",\\"type\\":\\"paragraph\\",\\"props\\":{\\"textColor\\":\\"default\\",\\"backgroundColor\\":\\"default\\",\\"textAlignment\\":\\"left\\"},\\"content\\":[{\\"type\\":\\"link\\",\\"href\\":\\"http://toxicology.ucsd.edu/Snakebite%20Protocols/Bothrops.htm\\",\\"content\\":[{\\"type\\":\\"text\\",\\"text\\":\\"http://toxicology.ucsd.edu/Snakebite%20Protocols/Bothrops.htm\\",\\"styles\\":{}}]},{\\"type\\":\\"text\\",\\"text\\":\\" *Click link above to access medical management protocol when at hospital.\\",\\"styles\\":{}}],\\"children\\":[]},{\\"id\\":\\"34704dd7-2e2e-4b1a-88a8-516f25d18347\\",\\"type\\":\\"paragraph\\",\\"props\\":{\\"textColor\\":\\"default\\",\\"backgroundColor\\":\\"default\\",\\"textAlignment\\":\\"left\\"},\\"content\\":[],\\"children\\":[]},{\\"id\\":\\"5f5fb652-1f30-43bf-9786-2fd858962c60\\",\\"type\\":\\"paragraph\\",\\"props\\":{\\"textColor\\":\\"default\\",\\"backgroundColor\\":\\"default\\",\\"textAlignment\\":\\"left\\"},\\"content\\":[{\\"type\\":\\"text\\",\\"text\\":\\"Go to the Hospital in Orotina:\\\\n\\",\\"styles\\":{\\"bold\\":true}},{\\"type\\":\\"link\\",\\"href\\":\\"https://maps.app.goo.gl/YLk4ey3v9SrHSSqe9\\",\\"content\\":[{\\"type\\":\\"text\\",\\"text\\":\\"https://maps