6c1cc64e-931e-4bed-8427-522b58af9828	getting-started	Getting Started	"[{\\"id\\":\\"a8155803-d279-41d7-b61d-9083eb65a360\\",\\"type\\":\\"paragraph\\",\\"props\\":{\\"textColor\\":\\"default\\",\\"backgroundColor\\":\\"default\\",\\"textAlignment\\":\\"left\\"},\\"content\\":[{\\"type\\":\\"text\\",\\"text\\":\\"Welcome to the Machuca Valley! This is a welcome guide that helps you to quickly navigate life here and points to the many resources we have already. The main digital resources are:\\\\n\\",\\"styles\\":{}}],\\"children\\":[]},{\\"id\\":\\"3ca3f258-2177-4524-9618-39e88d40ad2f\\",\\"type\\":\\"numberedListItem\\",\\"props\\":{\\"textColor\\":\\"default\\",\\"backgroundColor\\":\\"default\\",\\"textAlignment\\":\\"left\\"},\\"content\\":[{\\"type\\":\\"text\\",\\"text\\":\\"This Site!\\",\\"styles\\":{\\"bold\\":true}},{\\"type\\":\\"text\\",\\"text\\":\\" The idea here is to have a collection of communal wisdom organized as a wiki. The site only works if you actively participate and contribute as you discover knowledge.\\",\\"styles\\":{}}],\\"children\\":[]},{\\"id\\":\\"605880af-36df-456a-9b68-457806f6b664\\",\\"type\\":\\"numberedListItem\\",\\"props\\":{\\"textColor\\":\\"default\\",\\"backgroundColor\\":\\"default\\",\\"textAlignment\\":\\"left\\"},\\"content\\":[{\\"type\\":\\"text\\",\\"text\\":\\"Machuca Directory\\",\\"styles\\":{\\"bold\\":true}},{\\"type\\":\\"text\\",\\"text\\":\\"(see the tab on top) - this is the \\\\\\"Yellow Pages\\\\\\" of MV.  Feel free to add yourself there if you're offering some sort of a service.\\",\\"styles\\":{}}],\\"children\\":[]},{\\"id\\":\\"e9b246da-6341-4874-8339-da051f1a4d65\\",\\"type\\":\\"numberedListItem\\",\\"props\\":{\\"textColor\\":\\"default\\",\\"backgroundColor\\":\\"default\\",\\"textAlignment\\":\\"left\\"},\\"content\\":[{\\"type\\":\\"link\\",\\"href\\":\\"https://machucaelements.substack.com/\\",\\"content\\":[{\\"type\\":\\"text\\",\\"text\\":\\"Machhuca Elements Newsletter\\",\\"styles\\":{}}]